---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
&lt;section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"&gt;
  &lt;div class="absolute inset-0 z-0"&gt;
    &lt;img src="/media/hero-bg.jpg" alt="Космический фон" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60"/&gt;
    &lt;div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0A0A0F]/70 via-[#0A0A0F]/50 to-[#0A0A0F]"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="absolute inset-0 z-1 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none"&gt;
    &lt;div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary/40 animate-float"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="absolute top-1/3 right-1/4 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-secondary/30 animate-float delay-200"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="absolute bottom-1/3 left-1/3 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent/40 animate-float delay-300"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="absolute top-1/2 right-1/3 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-primary/60 animate-pulse-glow"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/2 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-secondary/50 animate-pulse-glow delay-200"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center"&gt;
    &lt;div class="mb-8 animate-fade-in-up"&gt;
      &lt;div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-full overflow-hidden ring-4 ring-primary/30 glow-primary"&gt;
        &lt;img src="/media/evgeniy.jpg" alt="Евгений Полиенко" class="w-full h-full object-cover"/&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 animate-fade-in-up delay-100"&gt;
      Путь к внутренней гармонии:
      &lt;span class="block gradient-text glow-text mt-2"&gt;от глубокого кризиса к осознанному управлению жизнью&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 animate-fade-in-up delay-200"&gt;
      Психология, духовные практики и коучинг для тех, кто готов к трансформации.
    &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 mb-10 animate-fade-in-up delay-200"&gt;
      &lt;div class="flex items-center gap-2"&gt;
        &lt;div class="flex gap-1"&gt;
          {[...Array(5)].map(() =&gt; (&lt;Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-400 fill-amber-400"/&gt;))}
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;span class="text-text-muted"&gt;4.9 из 5 на основе 127 отзывов&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="hidden md:block w-px h-6 bg-white/20"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-green-400"&gt;
        &lt;Icon name="lucide:thumbs-up" class="w-5 h-5"/&gt;
        &lt;span&gt;96% клиентов рекомендуют&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;a href="#services" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary rounded-full text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 glow-primary animate-fade-in-up delay-300"&gt;
      &lt;Icon name="lucide:calendar" class="w-5 h-5"/&gt;
      Записаться на консультацию
    &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce"&gt;
      &lt;Icon name="lucide:chevron-down" class="w-8 h-8 text-text-muted"/&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
